primary_asset_contracts.name: MultiverseVM
primary_asset_contracts.description:
Multiverse VM, a dynamic NFT with mechanisms to bring your NFT into the metaverse.

Each and every simulation that you own maintains links to other simulations generated upon the creation of the multiverse, and additional links/connection portals are generated via a combination of the owner address and the token seed, laying the foundations of a social NFT experience and forms the portal network for ＰＨΛＳΞ░２.

The multiverse VM is designed so owners can bring their existing NFTs in the multiverse, and allow holders to build extra experiences with their NFTs.

Tokens are designed to support extra URIs for each token holder, meaning that further expansion packs can be added to the token for extensibility, to experience Multiverse VM head to multiversevm.com
